Package: velocyto.R
Type: Package
Title: RNA velocity estimation in R 
Version: 0.6 
Date: 2018-04-29
Author: Peter Kharchenko
Maintainer: Peter Kharchenko <peter_kharchenko@hms.harvard.edu>
Description: Provides basic routines for estimation of gene-specific transcriptional derivatives and visualization of the resulting velocity patterns.
